{"tid":1625183,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急法令不管多少條通通無效， 我們只奉行愛港無罪抗暴有理!","createTime":"2019-10-05T06:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T06:15:45.000Z","uid":110259,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e2a7966737f507213392f4cffd1770ac3fc4048","tid":1625183,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"誠如大公報所說<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XFGv2wW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXFGv2wW.jpg&h=a9cfef0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc483c9f4abb209b64341cc3e5f0f8725c51ebd5","tid":1625183,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b33043dd0924c7b8eb7684d8b89e6be46f9f6658","tid":1625183,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:15:45.000Z","msg":"【行動核彈】你嘅幫手可以<span style=\"color: red;\">搞冧騰訊同埋新浪</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">強國人無得用微信微博</span>，順便<span style=\"color: red;\">搞冧深圳</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1620007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1620007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全民核彈！全部軍師立即響應美國，草擬制裁港共企業名單！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599761</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n制裁名單草稿（英文版）長文<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1607415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1607415</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國已經批准審核香港人權及民主法案2019，<span style=\"color: red;\">國會議員可以制定制裁名單。</span><br />\n請各位軍師善用呢個機會，<span style=\"color: gold;\">依家大家應搜集一切過往新聞片段、照片、新聞報導、政府新聞公告等一切資料，羅列所有協助侵犯香港人權嘅個人、企業嘅罪證</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">整理好一份名單，寄俾美國嘅國會議員</span>。"}]}